aparam api niṣphalavarjanāya prātimokṣoddiṣṭam ācaret ity āha. bhūmiphalakādiṣu nakhadaṇḍādinā rekhākarṣaṇalekhanādi niṣprayojanam āgatam āpatitaṃ vivarjayed bhagavatātra nivṛttir ājñapteti saṃsmṛtya, tadatikramavipākaphalabhayāt. tatkṣaṇam iti na tatra kālaparilambhaṃ kuryāt.

<commentary>saṃkleśasamudācāre saṃprajanyakāritāṃ yadety ādibhiḥ saptabhiḥ ślokaiḥ śikṣayitum āha.

prathamata eva svacittaṃ nirūpya. uktam. asaṃkliṣṭāvasthāyāṃ karaṇīyam uktam.</commentary>

etad eva darśayati. raktaṃ dviṣṭaṃ vā svacittaṃ yadā paśyet, tadā hastapādādicalanamātram api na kartavyam, nāpi vacanodīraṇam. anyathā tadutthāpite kāyavāgvijñapty api saṃkliṣṭe syātām.